download  script file and  go to your downloaded path with terminal and use 
$ sudo cp [script file name] /usr/local/bin   <==to use from any path
$ sudo cp mkfile /usr/local/bin
$ sudo cp chkdevice /usr/local/bin
$ sudo cp session /usr/local/bin
$ sudo cp numbers /usr/local/bin

